{
  "stem": "25178.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, Rika.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Which Rika?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, your cousin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Cousin?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, cousin from whom?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said she was Uncle Isaax's daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said here's a letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I read a letter that her husband, Bernard, had written to my uncle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the letter he wrote that he lived in the United States, in Culver City.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said that if he-- if my uncle knew of any Voorzangers still alive, to please to let him know [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so he could arrange to him-- to have them immigrate to the United States.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he would gladly sponsor it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me that letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in 1955.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, 1955.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Right away I wrote him, because to go emigrate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted to get out of Holland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had it with that country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, nothing but misfortunes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I wrote him a letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said OK, fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Told me what to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was going to pay for my trip, and for Freddy, my son.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Went to the consulate, and asked for a visa.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tried to get a visa under the refugee program, in the United States Immigration Department.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But it took so long that I started losing interest coming to the United States-- until 1956, when the Russians invaded Hungary.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother and I, we had made up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He came to visit me in the department store to say hello.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had made up, kind of.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my brother said to me-- I came-- I went to visit him in Belgium, [? or ?] he came to visit me in Holland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said get the hell out of here.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
